Packages 
Package Description
dungeon
Main classes of this project.
dungeon.commands
All commands the user can use in game.
dungeon.entity
Represents all entities you can see in the game, like players and other monsters.
dungeon.entity.monster
Represents all monsters entities you can see in the game.
dungeon.entity.types
Represents all Entity types.
dungeon.inventory
This part is for inventory management, treasure chest generation and monsters loots.
dungeon.inventory.spell
Here you can find all Spells you can be attack with or just you can use in an enumeration.
dungeon.rooms
Represents all rooms you can pass in the game, include room type and available direction enumerations.
